{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1272,"text":"Picture this:"},{"time":2649,"text":"It's Monday morning,"},{"time":3742,"text":"you're at the office,"},{"time":4861,"text":"you're settling in for the day at work,"},{"time":6615,"text":"and this guy that you sort of \nrecognize from down the hall,"},{"time":9437,"text":"walks right into your cubicle"},{"time":11273,"text":"and he steals your chair."},{"time":12675,"text":"Doesn't say a word —"},{"time":13917,"text":"just rolls away with it."},{"time":15305,"text":"Doesn't give you any information\nabout why he took your chair"},{"time":17788,"text":"out of all the other chairs \nthat are out there."},{"time":19899,"text":"Doesn't acknowledge the fact \nthat you might need your chair"},{"time":22041,"text":"to get some work done today."},{"time":23582,"text":"You wouldn't stand for \nit. You'd make a stink."},{"time":25839,"text":"You'd follow that guy\nback to his cubicle"},{"time":27866,"text":"and you'd say, \"Why my chair?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":31178,"text":"Okay, so now it's Tuesday morning\nand you're at the office,"},{"time":35299,"text":"and a meeting invitation pops \nup in your calendar."},{"time":38028,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":39633,"text":"And it's from this woman who you \nkind of know from down the hall,"},{"time":42709,"text":"and the subject line references some \nproject that you heard a little bit about."},{"time":46514,"text":"But there's no agenda."},{"time":48197,"text":"There's no information about why\nyou were invited to the meeting."},{"time":51273,"text":"And yet you accept the \nmeeting invitation, and you go."},{"time":55889,"text":"And when this highly \nunproductive session is over,"},{"time":58816,"text":"you go back to your desk,"},{"time":60499,"text":"and you stand at your \ndesk and you say,"},{"time":62008,"text":"\"Boy, I wish I had those two hours back,"},{"time":64671,"text":"like I wish I had my chair back.\""},{"time":66674,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":68180,"text":"Every day, we allow our coworkers,"},{"time":70751,"text":"who are otherwise very, \nvery nice people,"},{"time":72965,"text":"to steal from us."},{"time":74632,"text":"And I'm talking about something far \nmore valuable than office furniture."},{"time":78710,"text":"I'm talking about time. Your time."},{"time":81739,"text":"In fact, I believe that"},{"time":84392,"text":"we are in the middle\nof a global epidemic"},{"time":86877,"text":"of a terrible new illness\nknown as MAS:"},{"time":91917,"text":"Mindless Accept Syndrome."},{"time":94190,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":96084,"text":"The primary symptom of \nMindless Accept Syndrome\n"},{"time":98785,"text":"is just accepting a meeting invitation\nthe minute it pops up in your calendar."},{"time":102705,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":103975,"text":"It's an involuntary reflex — ding, \nclick, bing — it's in your calendar,"},{"time":107643,"text":"\"Gotta go, I'm already late \nfor a meeting.\" (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":110936,"text":"Meetings are important, right?"},{"time":113323,"text":"And collaboration is key to \nthe success of any enterprise."},{"time":116269,"text":"And a well-run meeting can yield \nreally positive, actionable results."},{"time":119662,"text":"But between globalization"},{"time":121420,"text":"and pervasive information technology,"},{"time":123735,"text":"the way that we work"},{"time":125406,"text":"has really changed dramatically \nover the last few years."},{"time":128635,"text":"And we're miserable. (Laughter)"},{"time":131842,"text":"And we're miserable not because the \nother guy can't run a good meeting,"},{"time":135382,"text":"it's because of MAS, our \nMindless Accept Syndrome,"},{"time":138194,"text":"which is a self-inflicted wound."}]},{"cues":[{"time":141970,"text":"Actually, I have evidence to prove\nthat MAS is a global epidemic."},{"time":147117,"text":"Let me tell you why."},{"time":148764,"text":"A couple of years ago, I put a video \non Youtube, and in the video,"},{"time":153036,"text":"I acted out every terrible \nconference call you've ever been on."},{"time":156234,"text":"It goes on for about five minutes,"},{"time":157893,"text":"and it has all the things that we \nhate about really bad meetings."},{"time":161084,"text":"There's the moderator who has \nno idea how to run the meeting."},{"time":164427,"text":"There are the participants who \nhave no idea why they're there."},{"time":166985,"text":"The whole thing kind of collapses\ninto this collaborative train wreck."},{"time":170688,"text":"And everybody leaves very angry."},{"time":173114,"text":"It's kind of funny."},{"time":174903,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":176486,"text":"Let's take a quick look."},{"time":178638,"text":"(Video) Our goal today is to come to an \nagreement on a very important proposal."},{"time":182465,"text":"As a group, we need to decide if —"},{"time":184552,"text":"bloop bloop —"},{"time":187331,"text":"Hi, who just joined?"},{"time":190898,"text":"Hi, it's Joe. I'm working from home today."},{"time":193910,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":195800,"text":"Hi, Joe. Thanks for \njoining us today, great."},{"time":198868,"text":"I was just saying, we have a lot of people \non the call we'd like to get through,"},{"time":201658,"text":"so let's skip the roll call \n"},{"time":203292,"text":"and I'm gonna dive right in."},{"time":205965,"text":"Our goal today is to come to an \nagreement on a very important proposal."},{"time":209840,"text":"As a group, we need to decide if —"},{"time":212405,"text":"bloop bloop —"},{"time":213698,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":215161,"text":"Hi, who just joined?"},{"time":217184,"text":"No? I thought I heard a beep. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":221993,"text":"Sound familiar?"},{"time":223629,"text":"Yeah, it sounds familiar \nto me, too."},{"time":225606,"text":"A couple of weeks after I put that online,"},{"time":227662,"text":"500,000 people in dozens of countries,"},{"time":230463,"text":"I mean dozens of countries,"},{"time":232103,"text":"watched this video."},{"time":233287,"text":"And three years later, it's still getting \nthousands of views every month."},{"time":236641,"text":"It's close to about a million right now."},{"time":238608,"text":"And in fact, some of the biggest\ncompanies in the world,"},{"time":240616,"text":"companies that you've \nheard of but I won't name,"},{"time":242526,"text":"have asked for my permission to use \nthis video in their new-hire training"},{"time":246421,"text":"to teach their new employees how \nnot to run a meeting at their company."},{"time":250670,"text":"And if the numbers —"},{"time":252155,"text":"there are a million views and it's\nbeing used by all these companies —"},{"time":254536,"text":"aren't enough proof that we have \na global problem with meetings,"},{"time":258062,"text":"there are the many, many thousands"},{"time":259839,"text":"of comments posted online"},{"time":261459,"text":"after the video went up."},{"time":263647,"text":"Thousands of people wrote things like,"},{"time":265621,"text":"\"OMG, that was my day today!\""},{"time":267475,"text":"\"That was my day every day!\""},{"time":269438,"text":"\"This is my life.\""},{"time":270597,"text":"One guy wrote,"},{"time":271527,"text":"\"It's funny because it's true."},{"time":273066,"text":"Eerily, sadly, depressingly true."},{"time":274973,"text":"It made me laugh until I cried."},{"time":276691,"text":"And cried. And I cried some more.\""},{"time":279441,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":281073,"text":"This poor guy said,"},{"time":282534,"text":"\"My daily life until \nretirement or death, sigh.\""},{"time":287611,"text":"These are real quotes"},{"time":289011,"text":"and it's real sad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":290810,"text":"A common theme running through\nall of these comments online"},{"time":293633,"text":"is this fundamental belief \nthat we are powerless"},{"time":296174,"text":"to do anything other \nthan go to meetings"},{"time":298075,"text":"and suffer through these \npoorly run meetings"},{"time":300453,"text":"and live to meet another day."},{"time":302542,"text":"But the truth is, we're \nnot powerless at all."},{"time":305683,"text":"In fact, the cure for MAS\nis right here in our hands."},{"time":308792,"text":"It's right at our fingertips, literally."},{"time":310977,"text":"It's something that I call ¡No MAS!"},{"time":314238,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":316468,"text":"Which, if I remember my \nhigh school Spanish,"},{"time":318866,"text":"means something like, \n\"Enough already, make it stop!\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":321657,"text":"Here's how No MAS \nworks. It's very simple."},{"time":324409,"text":"First of all, the next time you \nget a meeting invitation"},{"time":327606,"text":"that doesn't have a lot \nof information in it at all,"},{"time":330453,"text":"click the tentative button!"},{"time":332293,"text":"It's okay, you're allowed, \nthat's why it's there."},{"time":334743,"text":"It's right next to the accept button."},{"time":336252,"text":"Or the maybe button, or whatever button \nis there for you not to accept immediately."},{"time":339846,"text":"Then, get in touch with the person\nwho asked you to the meeting."},{"time":343629,"text":"Tell them you're very excited \nto support their work,"},{"time":346215,"text":"ask them what the goal \nof the meeting is,"},{"time":348230,"text":"and tell them you're interested in learning \nhow you can help them achieve their goal."},{"time":351917,"text":"And if we do this often enough,"},{"time":353845,"text":"and we do it respectfully,"},{"time":355183,"text":"people might start to be \na little bit more thoughtful"},{"time":357220,"text":"about the way they put together\nmeeting invitations."},{"time":359682,"text":"And you can make more thoughtful \ndecisions about accepting it."},{"time":362534,"text":"People might actually start \nsending out agendas. Imagine!"},{"time":365794,"text":"Or they might not have a conference call\nwith 12 people to talk about a status"},{"time":369542,"text":"when they could just do a quick\nemail and get it done with."},{"time":372825,"text":"People just might start to change their \nbehavior because you changed yours."},{"time":377659,"text":"And they just might bring\nyour chair back, too. (Laughter)"},{"time":381144,"text":"No MAS!"},{"time":382519,"text":"Thank you."},{"time":383959,"text":"(Applause)."}]}]}